    This code contains actions in Python3, so this grammar only works (supposedly) for the Python3 target. Please add this desc.xml file to declare this. Otherwise, nothing gets tested, and people will be saying "Why doesn't this compile for Java?"

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?>
<desc xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../_scripts/desc.xsd">
   <targets>Python3</targets>
   <inputs>examples/**/*.kum</inputs>
